    <p><strong>Exercise 3: Typing Practice Sequence</strong><br>
    Open a Japanese text input field (Google, your notes app, or our <a href="/japanese/tools/kana-quiz/">Kana Quiz</a>) and type these words in sequence. Focus on speed and accuracy:</p>
    <ol style="line-height: 2.2;">
      <li>がっこう (gakkou) — double your k: ga-k-kou</li>
